                </FooterDetails>
                <Header>Key Issues</Header>
                <Paragraph>The "Key Issues" web pages allow visitors to explore the GAO's work on a range of national issues by agency or topic. The agency's most relevant reports are highlighted on these web pages.</Paragraph>
            </EntitySourceOfInformation>
